56
00:03:05,602 --> 00:03:08,438
Let's win this thing.

57
00:03:09,523 --> 00:03:13,193
I got this far,
so I'll do my best and win.

58
00:03:14,277 --> 00:03:16,279
The Battle of Gods.

59
00:03:16,363 --> 00:03:19,324
