SUPPLEMENT BUSINESS WITH
ANNUAL SALES OF 400 BILLION WON

82
00:04:12,419 --> 00:04:15,797
CEO WHO DROVE
MULTI-BILLION-WON GROWTH

83
00:04:15,881 --> 00:04:17,090
THE SECOND FATE TO READ
LYUH ESTHER

84
00:04:17,174 --> 00:04:18,675
- She's beautiful.
- Gosh.

85
00:04:18,758 --> 00:04:20,469
