102
00:05:10,811 --> 00:05:12,604
That's what I'd like to know.

103
00:05:12,687 --> 00:05:14,606
They will send chills
down your spine today.

104
00:05:14,689 --> 00:05:16,316
- I guarantee it.
- Okay.

105
