is quite new too.

129
00:06:33,435 --> 00:06:36,938
Monad, please begin your reading.

130
00:06:38,273 --> 00:06:41,192
I think Sobin's a strong contender to win.

131
00:06:41,735 --> 00:06:44,321
But I'm confident too.

132
00:06:45,530 --> 00:06:48,241
I'm 120% confident about my tarot reading.

133
00:06:49,034 --> 00:06:50,452
There must be

134
