so that you can do something new.

149
00:07:46,424 --> 00:07:50,303
All of these cards represent
your current state.

150
00:07:50,387 --> 00:07:52,097
Here's what you're doing now.

151
00:07:52,180 --> 00:07:53,431
Number 1.

152
00:07:55,642 --> 00:07:57,018
- A map?
- Yes.

153
00:07:57,102 --> 00:07:58,937
- Oh…
- You go abroad.

154
00:07:59,020 --> 00:08:00,522
It means you're going abroad.

155
00:08:00,605 --> 00:08:02,482
CAREER
OR BUSINESS EXPANDING OVERSEAS

156
00:08:02,565 --> 00:08:04,526
- Ooh.
- Oh!

157
00:08:04,609 --> 00:08:05,985
