158
00:08:06,069 --> 00:08:07,362
2025, AGED 61, VENTURED ABROAD,

159
00:08:07,445 --> 00:08:09,114
INCREASING ANNUAL SALES
TO 400 BILLION WON

160
00:08:09,197 --> 00:08:11,825
This means 3 countries. And this is Japan.

161
00:08:13,868 --> 00:08:16,121
You can't stay in just 1 place.

162
00:08:16,204 --> 00:08:19,916
You need to move forward
in all 3 locations.

163
00:08:20,875 --> 00:08:22,252
How are you so on-point?

164
00:08:23,336 --> 00:08:24,504
She seems surprised.

165
00:08:26,089 --> 00:08:28,967
- I'm running a business right now.
- Yes.

166
00:08:29,050 --> 00:08:31,219
