- I see.

169
00:08:37,475 --> 00:08:40,562
-We only have a factory in the US.
-Okay.

170
00:08:40,645 --> 00:08:42,105
My goodness.

171
00:08:42,188 --> 00:08:44,149
2025, AGED 61, EXPANDING BUSINESS,
MAINLY IN THE US, CHINA, AND JAPAN

172
00:08:44,232 --> 00:08:46,943
She invested
20 to 30 billion won in the US.

173
00:08:47,027 --> 00:08:48,111
The US is a big deal.

174
00:08:49,362 --> 00:08:51,614
We spent a large fortune to set up

175
00:08:51,698 --> 00:08:54,367
