how I should expand my business there.

178
00:09:10,675 --> 00:09:12,761
From what I see…

179
00:09:18,308 --> 00:09:22,479
I already see an opportunity there,
but things will gain actual momentum

180
00:09:22,562 --> 00:09:25,315
