and a change in your business name.

183
00:09:30,278 --> 00:09:32,072
Your business will expand like crazy then.

184
00:09:34,032 --> 00:09:37,869
You'll advance at an incredible speed.

185
00:09:37,952 --> 00:09:42,791
Riding an elephant means
you advance and expand even faster.

186
00:09:42,874 --> 00:09:47,170
So, in my opinion, about 3 years from now,

187
00:09:47,253 --> 00:09:51,549
you'll reap the results you want.

188
00:09:51,633 --> 00:09:53,343
Oh, that's great news.

189
00:09:53,927 --> 00:09:55,345
- She seems confident.
- Yes.

190
00:09:55,428 --> 00:09:57,722
Tarot readings are so detailed.

191
00:09:57,806 --> 00:09:58,890
Yes, they are.

192
00:09:59,766 --> 00:10:02,602
If I hadn't pulled this card today,

193
00:10:02,685 --> 00:10:05,063
