-Okay.

194
00:10:05,146 --> 00:10:07,524
But this card shows infinity, zero limits.

195
00:10:08,691 --> 00:10:10,318
- Infinity?
- It means "limitless."

196
00:10:10,401 --> 00:10:11,820
