01:04:54,307 --> 01:04:55,308
Your matchup--

1286
01:04:55,391 --> 01:04:57,060
- I really hated to drop 1 of them.
- Me too.

1287
01:04:57,143 --> 01:05:00,355
It's 1 of those unlucky years for me.
My age ends in 9.

1288
01:05:00,438 --> 01:05:04,818
Manshin Kwon Sujin's
Battle of Fates ends here.

1289
01:05:04,901 --> 01:05:07,862
- Still, I made it pretty far.
- Thank you for your efforts.

1290
01:05:07,946 --> 01:05:10,907
This was a good opportunity
to meet many great fortune-tellers.

1291
01:05:10,990 --> 01:05:12,367
While watching the others,

1292
01:05:12,450 --> 01:05:16,287
I could learn what I could improve on.

1293
01:05:16,371 --> 01:05:19,082
I got to let go a lot
but also learn a lot too.

1294
01:05:20,250 --> 01:05:21,543
I guess
my Granny spirit's turning this

1295
01:05:21,626 --> 01:05:22,627
into a magnificent story for me.

1296
01:05:22,710 --> 01:05:24,170
I got this far.

1297
01:05:24,254 --> 01:05:26,297
If I make it to the finals,

1298
01:05:26,381 --> 01:05:27,590
I want to show the world.

1299
01:05:27,674 --> 01:05:28,800
I have to win no matter what.

1300
01:05:28,883 --> 01:05:31,344
My Granny spirit must have
a grand plan for me.

1301
01:05:31,427 --> 01:05:32,512
A proud winner.

1302
01:05:32,595 --> 01:05:33,596
I'll win.

1303
01:05:33,680 --> 01:05:34,681
Let's win.

1304
01:05:36,891 --> 01:05:37,892
What's this?

1305
01:05:39,686 --> 01:05:43,565
So they need to summon
the deceased to this place right now?

1306
01:05:44,816 --> 01:05:45,817
This is it.

1307
01:05:45,900 --> 01:05:47,986
I'm confident I won't lose.

1308
01:05:48,069 --> 01:05:50,029
- What do you know?
- What?

1309
01:05:50,113 --> 01:05:52,824
Look how angry Granny is, you fool!

1310
01:05:52,907 --> 01:05:54,659
What? What's happening?

1311
01:05:54,742 --> 01:05:56,327
-She's possessed.
-That's why…

1312
01:05:56,411 --> 01:05:57,871
She needs an exorcism.

1313
01:05:57,954 --> 01:05:59,873
Granny, Grandpa!

1314
01:05:59,956 --> 01:06:01,416
I feel like I'm going to die.

1315
01:06:01,499 --> 01:06:02,500
Oh, no!

1316
01:06:02,584 --> 01:06:04,836
"My Granny spirit is furious."
It was so painful.

1317
01:06:08,298 --> 01:06:09,841
It's not fair!

1318
01:07:10,401 --> 01:07:12,403
Translated by Jennifer Jean Lim
